Actually, I kind of like the name Jakarta-town. It allows the reader to sit back and chuckle every time he sees it, and ponder the stupidity of the all-mighty leader who decided to name is capitol city A) a town and B) after himself in such a stupid fashion. Just one of those little jokes that are fun to put in there.

Tevildo - pretty serious guy
Bjorn - serious guy
Hightower - semi-serious guy
Trahern - joker kind of guy, changes if something important is happening
Shifter- VERY serious guy

That's what its going to be so far. Now some RPG fans want a really serious book, but since this is fanfic it should have some comedy too, right?

-Zjack
